If you have received the goods before you withdraw your order, then you must send them back to The Telegraph Bookshop return address at your own cost and risk, unless the goods were supplied faulty or damaged. If you withdraw your order but The Telegraph Bookshop have already processed the goods for despatch and you have yet to receive them, you must not unpack the goods when they are received by you and you must send the goods back to The Telegraph Bookshop return address at your own cost and risk as soon as possible.<br />
